history.content:
Registration for our free Womxn in Tech Conference on Feb 12-13 is now OPEN at https://womxnintech.github.io/! If you’re a womxn or other underrepresented minority in tech, come join us for a great opportunity to meet industry recruiters in 1-on-1 sessions and engage in professional development workshops!
    Resume drop will be available upon registration. Again, this conference is completely virtual and free! Whether you’re searching for a job, want to gain more insight into the recruiting process, or are looking to improve your resume content and interviewing skills, we look forward to seeing you next week!
history.subject: Womxn in Tech Conference Registration now open!: 1:1s with DE Shaw, Nvidia, Bloomberg and more!
